description:
The daring James Bond is back in a definitive bumper edition collecting the second period of Jim Lawrence's celebrated run in comic strip form! Includes nine of Bonds most thrilling and dangerous missions: Trouble Spot, Isle of Condors, The League of Vampires, Die With My Boots On, The Girl Machine, Beware of Butterflies, The Nevsky Nude, The Phoenix Project and The Black Ruby Caper.

All stories were originally printed in the Daily Express newspaper between 1971 and 1975.
name: Volume 004

description: Rich, decadent, delicious, and a little bit dangerous, this heapin' helpin' of Meat Cake is sure to satisfy even the most discriminating palate! Dig in to these tales of depravity, violence, pyromania, and obsession. Dig in to these tales of depravity, violence, pyromania, and obsession with Richard Dirt, Wax Wolf, Hindrance and Perfida, Friend the Girl, Strega Pez and a host of others! Stories such as "Bullets for Breakfast," "Demon Drink," "Twist of Fate," and "Cozy Corner" add up to one of the most unique offerings in comics.
